metadata.name: chemical girl
metadata.description:
a tribute to Avril15

an illustration created for Avril15 fanart competition, visuals of a young girl defending the earth against AI bots and its chemical (pollution, war, hatred, racism), that goes to show that what we do/created today will define tomorrow (our younger generations). if we tolerate this, our children will be next (says The Manic Street Preachers) so, LOVE one another :)

size: 4618px x 6618px
